This project (Orin) is a CI/CD tool for automating update server-side's services.

It requires a valid JDK installation(JDK 22 or above) to run, and in most cases, a valid network port is required for Github webhooks.

For it's old GoLang implementation, see https://github.com/glowingstone124/GoCi.

Its name was inspired from Kaenbyou Rin, a character from Touhou Project.

